   - Surface: #ffffff (cards, dialogs)
   - Background: #fafafa (page background)
   - Text: rgba(0,0,0,0.87) primary, rgba(0,0,0,0.60) secondary

4. **FAB Floating Action Button**
   - Circular button: width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 50%;
