Accent colors (minimal use):
- Blue: #0066ff (links, primary actions)
- Black: #000000 (emphasis)
- Red: #ff0000 (warnings, delete)

**Key CSS Class Examples**

\`\`\`css
/* Minimalist Container */
.minimal-container {
