#### 3.4 Skeuomorphic Switch (.skeuo-switch)
*A realistic physical toggle switch with clear on/off states and mechanical feel.*

```html
<!-- Switch Base -->
<label class="
  relative inline-flex items-center cursor-pointer
  w-20 h-10 rounded-full
  /* Recessed Base Track */
  bg-[#1a2634]
